{"view":"article","slug":"clock-7-simul","category":"Clock","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Clock","title":{"en":"魔表7-Simul教程"},"content":{"en":"<p><strong>魔表7-Simul教程</strong></p><p>本教程给出7-Simul 法的Tommy Cherry不翻面版本.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p><strong>观察记号</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"4\"><p>开始记忆的面上的轮用小写字母，反面的用大写字母. 这里假设开始记忆的面为白面. 用x2翻面. </p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>dl</p><p>d</p><p>r</p><p>l</p><p>u</p><p>c</p><p>dr</p><p>ur</p><p>ul</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>L</p><p>D</p><p>R</p><p>U</p><p>C</p><p>DR</p><p>DL</p><p>UR</p><p>UL</p></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>从X轮到T轮的<strong>黄箭头</strong>: 表示从X到T的点数T←X, 本文中用记号T-X表示, 即Y相对于X的点数, 建议取值范围为-6到+6之间的整数,其中用正负数表示顺逆时针. 注: 也等价于T的点数减去X的点数, 但实操中不使用减法. 运算均在模12意义下进行, 例如-1和11是等价的. 从某箭头到Z轮的<strong>红箭头</strong>: 表示将某箭头对应的数字加到Z轮上. <strong>红加号</strong>: 数字相加. 图中箭头有可能出现层叠, 应从底层依次运算到顶层.</p><p><strong>转动记号</strong></p><p>大写字母代表抬起对应立柱. 小写代表放下对应立柱, 抬起所有其他立柱. 有序数对由2个数字构成, 左侧和右侧数字分别代表左上轮和右上轮. 例外: dl(x,y)中左侧和右侧数字分别代表左下轮和右上轮, DR(x,y)中左侧和右侧数字分别代表左上轮和右下轮.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>UR1+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>DR6+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>DL4-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>UL1-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R3+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>D1-</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>L4-</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>U2+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>ALL5+</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>y2</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>x2</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>z</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>dl(1+,3-)</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R(3+,4+)</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>\\(3+,6+)</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>DR(1+,2+)</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>dl1+</strong></p></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>观察</strong></p><p>(可选) 转体, 使得M1=c-d最小. 依次计算并记忆M1~M6. (可选) 为方便记忆, 将M1~M6中的负数转化为字母: </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p>-1</p></td><td><p>-2</p></td><td><p>-3</p></td><td><p>-4</p></td><td><p>-5</p></td><td><p>-6</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>a</p></td><td><p>b</p></td><td><p>c</p></td><td><p>d</p></td><td><p>e</p></td><td><p>f</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>   </strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>Z</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>M1=c-d</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>M2=(dr-r)+(U-L)</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>M3=d-r</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>M4=L-U</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>   </strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>   </strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>Z</p><p>Z</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>M5=UR-U+C-D+l-ul+r</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>M6=(u-c+d)+(UL-L)+(DR-R)</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>还原</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>M2</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>M3</strong></p><p><strong>M4</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>X→T</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>M5</strong></p><p><strong>M6</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p><strong>M1</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p><strong>Y→T</strong></p><p>T</p><p>Y</p><p>T</p><p>X</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"dl(M1, M2)\">dl(M1, M2)</span></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>R(M3,M4)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>DR(X</strong>→<strong>T,Y</strong>→<strong>T)</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>\\(M5,M6)</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>X→T</strong></p><p><strong>Y→T</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>X→T</strong></p><p><strong>Y→T</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>X→12</strong></p><p><strong>Y→12</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p>X</p><p>X</p><p>X</p><p>Y</p><p>T</p><p>X</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image50.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p>X</p><p>X</p><p>X</p><p>X+</p><p>Y</p><p>T</p><p>X</p><p>X</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image52.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p><p>X</p><p>X</p><p>X</p><p>X</p><p>X</p><p>X</p><p>X</p><p>X</p><p>Y</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>UL(X</strong>→<strong>T,Y</strong>→<strong>T)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>L(X</strong>→<strong>T,Y</strong>→<strong>T)</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>DR(X</strong>→<strong>12,Y</strong>→<strong>12)</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>实例</strong></p><p>2.96 Volodymyr Kapustianskyi <a href=\"https://clockdb.net/r/459\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://clockdb.net/r/459</a></p><p>打乱: 黑面12点朝上开始 UR3- DR2- DL1+ UL2- U6+ R4- D1- L5+ ALL4+ y2 U3+ R1+ D4- L1- ALL1+</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td></td><td><p><img alt=\"徽标, 图标\n\nAI 生成的内容可能不正确。\" src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image53.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>   </strong><img alt=\"图标\n\nAI 生成的内容可能不正确。\" src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image54.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>从黑面12点朝上开始观察. M1=c-d=1. M2=(dr-r)+(U-L)=1+(-4)=-3. M3=d-r=3. M4=L-U=4. </p><p>M5=UR-U+C-D+l-ul+r=2+6-D+l-ul+r=8-10+l-ul+r=(-2)+1-ul+r=(-1)-ul+r=11-ul+r=11-8+0=3.</p><p>M6=(u-c+d)+(UL-L)+(DR-R)=(2+3)+0+1=6.</p><p>解法: z2 dl(1+,3-) R(3+,4+) DR(3-,3-) \\(3+,6+) UL(4+,6+) L(5-,5+) ur(0+,2-)</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image55.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image56.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image57.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image58.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>z2</p></td><td><p>dl(1+,3-)</p></td><td><p>R(3+,4+)</p></td><td><p>DR(3-,3-)</p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image59.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image60.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image61.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image62.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>\\(3+,6+)</p></td><td><p>UL(4+,6+)</p></td><td><p>L(5-,5+)</p></td><td><p>ur(0+,2-)</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>更多实例</strong></p><p>2.46 Volodymyr Kapustianskyi</p><p>Scramble: UR5- DR0+ DL2- UL5+ U2+ R3+ D3- L0+ ALL3+ y2 U2+ R6+ D3+ L0+ ALL4+</p><p>Solution: x2 z' dl6+ R(3+,4-) DR(1+,2+) \\(5+,6+) UL(3-,3+) L(4-,4-) ur(5-,6+)</p><p>2.24 Volodymyr Kapustianskyi</p><p>Scramble: UR6+ DR6+ DL4+ UL3+ U4+ R5+ D2+ L1+ ALL3- y2 U0+ R4+ D2- L2- ALL5-</p><p>Solution: dl1+ R(5+,6+) DR(5+,2+) \\(3-,1+) UL(0+,3-) L(2+,5-) ur(3-,1+)</p><p>2.24 Volodymyr Kapustianskyi</p><p>Scramble: UR2+ DR2- DL3+ UL4+ U2- R0+ D0+ L3+ ALL6+ y2 U0+ R3- D5+ L5+ ALL1-</p><p>Solution: z' dl1+ R(4+,0+) DR5- \\(6-,1-) UL(3+,2-) L(3-,3+) ur(4+,2-)</p><p>2.43 Volodymyr Kapustianskyi</p><p>Scramble: UR5- DR6+ DL2- UL2+ U0+ R1- D4+ L0+ ALL5+ y2 U6+ R4- D1+ L3- ALL6+</p><p>Solution: z dl1- R(4-,2+) DR(2+,4+) \\(6-,5-) UL(3+,5-) L(4-,3-) ur4-</p><p><strong>参考资料</strong></p><p>Dan Boharon. 7 Simul (no-flip) Tutorial <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1uqROrP4tHa5fv7dlrNsvw1RgwLj6VxmL\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1uqROrP4tHa5fv7dlrNsvw1RgwLj6VxmL</a></p>"},"algs":["dl(M1, M2)"],"thumb":"/stats/alg/media/clock-7-simul/en/image2.svg","warningCount":3,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
